<!--  CONTENT -->

<tr>
<td colspan="3">
<div id="sectionDescription">The User List not only displays a list of all users currently logged on to the Wonderland server, but it also provides a host of other features for communicating with users and with groups. </div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>

<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-1.png" align="top">
The User List will automatically open when you start Wonderland.
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/UserList.png"></div>
<div id="stepNoHang">
The people with names in blue are in speaking range of you. Square brackets around a name indicate that the person is on mute and three dots after their name indicate that they are speaking.</div>
</div>
</td>

<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-2.png" align="top">
Select the name of a person to communicate with that person, raise or lower their volume, or find them in the world.
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/UserListUserSelected.png"></div>
</td>

<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-3.png" align="top">
Click on a tool to initiate communication or change settings. Here's what each icon means:<br><br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListMuteOff24x24.png"> Mute<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListChatText24x24.png"> Text Chat<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListChatVoice24x24.png"> Voice Chat<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListPhone24x24.png"> Phone<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListGoto24x24.png"> Go To User<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListEdit24x24.png"> Edit User Name<br>
<img src="UserList/UserListIcons/UserListProperties24x24.png"> Edit User Properties<br><br>
<div id="stepNoHang">
The "Edit User Name" button is only enabled when you select your own name. The "Edit User Properties" setting allows you to change the size of avatar names or hide the names entirely.</div>
</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>

<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-4.png" align="top">
To communicate with a group of users, click on the "groups" tab.
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/GroupsList.png"></div>
<div id="stepNoHang">
Members of the "admin" group may see all communications initiated using this list.</div>
</div>
</td>

<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-5.png" align="top">
To chat with a whole group, select the group name from the list and click on the Text Chat button. Type your text in the field at the bottom of the window and click "Send."
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/GroupChat.png" width="200px"></div>
<div id="stepNoHang">
These group chats are saved, so you can scroll back to review any conversation that might have happened before you opened the chat window.</div>
</div>
</td>


<td>
<div id="step">
<img src="BlueNumbers/Blue-6.png" align="top">
To send a broadcast message to a group, click on a group  name and then click the icon farthest to the right. Type in your message and click "Send."
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/UserListBroadcastSend.png" width="200px"></div>
<div id="stepNoHang">
A window will pop up on all group member screens with your message.</div>
<div id="pix"><img src="UserList/UserListBroadcastRcv.png" width="200px"></div>
<div id="stepNoHang">
Broadcast messages are archived in the corresponding group chat transcript.</div>
</div>
</td>


</tr>


</table>